cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper involves deep reinforcement learning and generative adversarial imitation learning to train controllers for high-dimensional humanoid bodies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). It also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it deals with controlling humanoid bodies. Computer vision (cs.CV) is also relevant as it involves analyzing motion capture data. Additionally, it involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with training neural network policies. Finally, it involves systems and control (cs.SY) as it deals with controlling a complex system (humanoid body) to perform tasks.
